hes!  4 oz.  \u003cem\u003e \u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"product-desc fl fw\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eOur Beauty Notes\u003c\/em\u003e: This favorite Indie Lee Cleanser is simple yet effective in skincare multitasking, its gel-like cleanser tackles stubborn eye makeup with one pump, while two pumps rid an entire face of makeup and dirt. With the ability to work as an exfoliator if left on to \"sit\" on the skin and smells like the things dreams are made off. Clear, bright and younger looking skin is in your future. \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"product-desc fl fw\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIndie Lee tugged at our heart strings initially with her story of overcoming a brain tumor to discover the link between conventional beauty and its potential health harm. After learning about her story, she then struck us with a genius product line that conquers disbelieve in clean beauty. Since regaining her health, she has taken the clean beauty world by storm creating the chic, effective and modern (right up our alley!): Indie Lee.\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch5 style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eIngredients \u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/h5\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003ePurified Water, Decyl Glucoside (Veg. Oils \u0026amp; Sugar), Disodium Coco-Glucoside Citrate, Coco Glucoside Oleaste (Coconut and Sunflower Oil), Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Xanthan Gum, Fragaria Chiloensis Seed Oil (Strawberry), Lycopene, Phenoxyethanol and Ethylhexylglycerin (both derived from natural sources). \u003c\/span\u003e \u003cem\u003e*Note: contains gluten. \u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch5\u003e\u003cem\u003eUse \u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/h5\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply a small amount of cleanser to wet face. Use with a wet cotton pad to remove eye makeup. Rinse completely with water. Follow with toner and moisturizer. For external use only. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cstyle\u003e\u003c!--\n.embed-container { 